  <ul>
      <li>Bachelor's degree in Computer Science or related field.</li>
      <li>Professional certification in web development.</li>
      <li>5+ years of experience in web development.</li>
      <li>Proficiency in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and frameworks like React or Angular.</li>
      <li>Strong problem-solving skills and attention to detail.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Preferred Skills</h2>
  <p>Experience with server-side languages such as Python or Ruby. Knowledge of database technologies like MySQL, Oracle, and MongoDB.</p>

  <h2>Benefits and Perks</h2>
